## Spacing (8px base)

```css
--space-1: 4px;
--space-2: 8px;
--space-3: 12px;
--space-4: 16px;
--space-5: 24px;
--space-6: 32px;
--space-7: 48px;
--space-8: 64px;
--space-9: 80px;
--space-10: 120px;
```

## Shape

```css
--radius-sm: 8px;
--radius-md: 12px;
--radius-lg: 16px;
--radius-xl: 20px;
--radius-full: 999px;
--shadow-sm: 0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
--shadow-md: 0 4px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
--ease-default: 0.2s ease;
```

## Hard Rules

- `--color-dark` for dark surfaces (NOT `#000000`)
- `--color-surface-secondary` for alternating warm sections
- Green (`--color-success`) only for verified badges and positive signals — never decorative
- Teal (`--color-teal-dark`) for structural accents, icons, borders
- Section padding desktop: `--space-9` (80px) standard, `--space-10` (120px) hero
- Section padding mobile: `--space-8` (64px) standard
- Container: max-width 1200px, padding `--space-5` desktop / `--space-4` mobile
- Grid gaps: always `--space-5`
- Card padding: always `--space-5`
